    {
      "label": "Container Security Hardening",
      "file_type": "rationale",
      "rationale": "Apply defense-in-depth and least-privilege to the production container: read-only root filesystem, dropped capabilities (cap_drop ALL), no-new-privileges, tmpfs for writable paths, and running as non-root UID 1000 to limit blast radius if the app or web server is compromised.",
